# Frontend Rules

Follow [`docs/frontend.md`](../../docs/frontend.md).

- Folder layout: `src/app/`, `pages/`, `layouts/`, `features/`, plus top-level `components/`, `hooks/`, `services/`, `contexts/`, `lib/`, `utils/`, `types/`, `constants/`.
- TanStack Query for all API/server state; AuthContext for session only.
- No raw Axios in components; use `services/` wrappers.
- Refresh token: HttpOnly cookie only — never `localStorage`.
